      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions (fixed base, axial-offset compressive load at 10 mm anterior offset) directly replicate F1717 test fixture geometry. Material inputs derived from same production lot as test samples. Friction coefficient sensitivity analysis conducted (mu=0.1–0.3); QoI sensitivity < 3%. Required level 3 met."
